      Text

      A fast-paced, deadline-driven method where buyers compete in real time. Auctions create urgency and suit properties in demand or when value is unclear. With no cooling-off period, sales are unconditional, providing certainty for both seller and buyer.

      Fixed Price

      Text

      A straightforward approach where the asking price is set from day one. Buyers know what窶冱 expected, and it typically suits properties in a competitive or price-sensitive market where clarity is key.

      Tender

      Text

      Buyers submit confidential written offers by a specified deadline, without knowing what others are offering. This process creates a level playing field and suits properties with unique appeal or when discretion is important.
